    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚海地援助团因致命抗议活动受到审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/kenya-s-mission-to-haiti-faces-scrutiny-after-deadly-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在400名肯尼亚警察抵达海地执行由美国支持的人道主义任务的同一天，他们在国内的同事却向医护人员发射催泪瓦斯，并向和平抗议者无差别射击，对反对增税的示威活动进行残酷镇压。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/kenya-s-mission-to-haiti-faces-scrutiny-after-deadly-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 09:59:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>五角大楼面临国会不愿解决的华为困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/pentagon-has-a-huawei-dilemma-congress-doesn-t-want-to-solve</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五角大楼面临一个问题：作为全球最大的雇主之一，如何避免与依赖中国华为技术有限公司（全球最大电信供应商）的公司做生意？]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/pentagon-has-a-huawei-dilemma-congress-doesn-t-want-to-solve</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 09:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>估计法国左翼计划的成本将是马克龙计划的六倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/french-left-s-plans-to-cost-six-times-macron-s-estimates-show</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据最新估算，参加法国立法议会选举的各政党做出的竞选承诺在成本上差异巨大，其中左翼联盟的承诺成本最高，主要体现在降低退休年龄的计划上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/french-left-s-plans-to-cost-six-times-macron-s-estimates-show</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 08:45:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>突尼斯总统选举定于 10 月 6 日举行，反对派分裂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/tunisia-sets-oct-6-for-presidential-vote-with-opposition-split</link>
      <description><![CDATA[突尼斯定于 10 月 6 日举行总统选举，这次选举可能成为这个北非国家民主的试金石，该国的民粹主义领导人已经掌握了广泛权力并压制了大多数异议人士。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/tunisia-sets-oct-6-for-presidential-vote-with-opposition-split</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 08:32:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国汽车城希望工党能推动电动汽车电池梦想</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/uk-s-motor-city-hopes-labour-can-jump-start-ev-battery-dream</link>
      <description><![CDATA[考文垂市宣布计划在英格兰西米德兰兹郡的小型机场建造一座巨型电动汽车电池工厂，迄今已过去三年多，这给人们带来了希望，即英国能够赶上在电池生产方面已经领先多年的竞争对手国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/uk-s-motor-city-hopes-labour-can-jump-start-ev-battery-dream</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞寻求多数席位，竞争对手联手阻止她</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/le-pen-seeks-majority-as-rival-groups-band-together-to-stop-her</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在周日举行的法国立法选举最后一轮中，玛丽娜·勒庞领导的国民联盟正在努力争取绝对多数，而竞争对手则在努力阻止极右翼政党掌权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/le-pen-seeks-majority-as-rival-groups-band-together-to-stop-her</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 07:27:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍里斯·约翰逊出人意料地采取最后行动，避免保守党被彻底击败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/boris-johnson-makes-surprise-late-move-to-avert-tory-wipeout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[鲍里斯·约翰逊 (Boris Johnson) 意外参与了英国大选活动，他敦促保守党选民阻止工党在里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 领导的保守党的最后一搏中取得压倒性胜利，以避免在周四的选举中遭受预计的巨大损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/boris-johnson-makes-surprise-late-move-to-avert-tory-wipeout</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 21:13:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国扣押台湾渔船或加剧紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/china-seizes-taiwan-fishing-boat-and-crew-as-tensions-simmer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国扣押了一艘台湾渔船及其船员，此举有可能加剧与台湾新总统的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/china-seizes-taiwan-fishing-boat-and-crew-as-tensions-simmer</guid>
